OL,3,CMemorials to be placed at site of mass
OL,4,Cgrave in Oldham
OL,6,FMemorial benches and plinths are being
OL,7,Fplaced in cemeteries to remember
OL,8,Fbabies, children and adults who were
OL,9,Fburied in unmarked graves.
OL,11,FPlinths ` each inscribed with a
OL,12,Fpoignant verse ` and benches where
OL,13,Frelatives and friends can sit
OL,14,Fpeacefully with their thoughts, will
OL,15,Fbe installed at seven council burial
OL,16,Fsites in Oldham.
OL,18,FThe remembrance spaces are in response
OL,19,Fto an unmarked burial site discovered
OL,20,Fin Royton in September.
