OL,3,CMemorials to be placed at site of mass
OL,4,Cgrave in Oldham
OL,6,FThe discovery was made by a woman from
OL,7,Fthe local area who was searching for
OL,8,Fthe last resting place of her twin
OL,9,Fbrothers, who died in 1962.
OL,11,FBefore the 1980s, stillborn babies
OL,12,Fwere sometimes taken away from their
OL,13,Fmother and families were often not
OL,14,Fgiven any details of where they were
OL,15,Fburied.
