OL,3,CMemorials to be placed at site of mass
OL,4,Cgrave in Oldham
OL,6,FCouncillor Arooj Shah, Leader of
OL,7,FOldham Council, said: "After listening
OL,8,Fto the views of the affected families
OL,9,Fwe believe having somewhere discreet
OL,10,Fat each burial site, where people can
OL,11,Fsit down and quietly reflect and
OL,12,Fremember is the best way.
OL,14,F"Hopefully families affected by the
OL,15,Finsensitive practices of the past can
OL,16,Fnow take some comfort knowing that
OL,17,Fsoon there will be a place for them to
OL,18,Fcome where their loss is acknowledged
OL,19,Fand remembered."
