OL,3,CMemorials to be placed at site of mass
OL,4,Cgrave in Oldham
OL,6,FCemetery staff will put the first
OL,7,Fmemorials in place over the coming
OL,8,Fweeks.
OL,10,FOldham Council is also offering
OL,11,Femotional support to relatives who've
OL,12,Frecently found out loved ones were
OL,13,Fburied without tributes.
OL,15,FDetails of the burial site in Royton,
OL,16,Fwhich brought this issue to public
OL,17,Fattention, have been available to
OL,18,Fresearch for some time and Council
OL,19,Fstaff have supported many families to
OL,20,Flocate their loved ones over the years.
