OL,3,CMemorials to be placed at site of mass
OL,4,Cgrave in Oldham
OL,6,FAnyone can search for their deceased
OL,7,Frelative by using the link on the
OL,8,Fcouncil website.
OL,10,FThe grave, numbered 1A-360 in Royton,
OL,11,Fwas first opened in 1924 and the last
OL,12,Fburial took place in 1972, the records
OL,13,Ffor the Royton public graves have now
OL,14,Fall been digitalised, and work is
OL,15,Fongoing for the other records to also
OL,16,Fbe put on line.
OL,18,FFamilies searching for their relatives
OL,19,Fwill need to know the surname and
OL,20,Fapproximate date of death.
